NALU
Hi, Mom. Where's Daddy?
EUNICE
Hi, dear. He's in the bedroom.
Nalu runs up the stairs. Cristina stays in the living room.
INT. PAIVA FAMILY HOME / MASTER BEDROOM - DAY
Nalu doesn't blink at finding two strangers with her father,
who's putting on a tie and struggles to act naturally.
