Eunice heads up to the study. The Men watch her go.
35.
36.
INT. PAIVA FAMILY HOME / STUDY - LATE AT NIGHT
Trying not to make any noise, Eunice rummages through the
desk drawers in search of any potentially suspicious
material. All she finds is an address book, papers from
Rubens' work, a few sketches and handwritten notes.
She picks up some scattered photos and puts them into a box
