Eunice grabs her arm and raises her voice.
EUNICE
You're the only person who saw him
in there. I need your help. If I
can't prove he was arrested--
Two NUNS come into the chapel. Caught off guard, Martha
smiles abruptly and hands Eunice a prayer booklet.
MARTHA
Please, Eunice, you've got to
leave.
EUNICE
My husband's in danger, Martha.
MARTHA
We're all in danger.
Martha goes over toward the Nuns. Eunice drops the booklet on
a pew and hurries out.
I/E. RUBENS'S OPEL KADETT - DAY
Eunice smokes as she drives, glancing nervously into the rear-
view mirror. Next to her, Eliana bounces a restless leg.
In the backseat, Marcelo plays with their father's oversized
hard hat. Nalu is talking loudly.
NALU
I've missed rehearsals. Cris said I
can go with her.
57.
58.
