Boca opens the last drawer and cackles.
BOCA (CONT'D)
Son of a bitch.
He pulls out a bottle of imported whiskey.
BOCA (CONT'D)
Do you mind? I'll buy him another.
Eunice shakes her head and lights a cigarette. Boca pours two
glasses with ice.
BOCA (CONT'D)
You sure you don't want to stop by
