at the vastness of the sea, invisible in the dark of night.
EXT. PLOT OF LAND IN JARDIM BOTÂNICO - MORNING
A stake is ripped out of the dirt. Then another.
Eunice grabs a third stake, marking the bounds of the house
that will never be completed, and rips it up furiously. A
fourth stake, stuck deep into the earth, resists.
Eunice keeps on until she yanks it out, and dusts off her
hands without dirtying her dress.
INT. ENGINEERING FIRM / RUBENS' OFFICE - DAY
There are new EMPLOYEES in the firm now, huddled around a
